name: Anagram Five.
description:
Augmented Reality Interface w/ 3D Model feat. Custom "Ghostly" Texture.
GLB

This piece was inspired by Japanese folklore about ningyo dolls and how as humans we anthropomorphize dolls into images of ourselves. "Why is it necessary to make robots in our own image? Is it possible to exist with forms of artificial intelligence without forcing them into the human mold?" - Mamoru Oshii
